\newlabel{fig:arch}{{1}{3}{Density-modulated additive steering architecture (Eq.~\ref {eq:hybrid}). Four acceleration components feed the accumulator unmodulated; the ORCA term is scaled by $w_o(\rho _i)=1-\sigma (\rho _i;\rho _0,k)$, with $\rho _i$ the local Voronoi-cell density. The sum $\mathbf {a}_i$ drives the Euler integrator to update $(\mathbf {v}_i,\mathbf {x}_i)$}{figure.caption.1}{}}
